sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AuthManager
    participant Database
    participant Client
    
    User->>AuthManager: Request Login (credentials)
    AuthManager->>Database: Validate User
    Database-->>AuthManager: User Valid
    AuthManager->>AuthManager: Generate Claims
    AuthManager->>AuthManager: Create JWT Token
    AuthManager->>AuthManager: Sign with HMAC-SHA256
    AuthManager-->>User: Return JWT Token
    User->>Client: Store JWT Token
    Client->>AuthManager: Request with JWT
    AuthManager->>AuthManager: Validate Token
    AuthManager->>AuthManager: Verify HMAC-SHA256
    AuthManager-->>Client: Token Valid
    Client-->>User: Grant Access     
